import React from 'react'; export default class enterprescription extends React.Component{ constructor(props){ super(props); this.handleChange=this.handleChange.bind(this); this.handleSubmit=this.handleSubmit.bind(this); this.state={ rsign:this.props.lens.rsign, lsign:this.props.lens.lsign, resph:this.props.lens.resph, reax:this.props.lens.reax, recyl:this.props.lens.recyl, readd:this.props.lens.readd, lesph:this.props.lens.lesph, leax:this.props.lens.leax, lecyl:this.props.lens.lecyl, leadd:this.props.lens.leadd } } handleChange(e){ const name=e.target.name; this.setState({[name]:e.target.value}); this.props.handleChange(e.target.name,e.target.value); } handleSubmit(e){ this.props.handleSubmit(); } render(){ return (
Sign SPH. CYL. AXIS ADD
RE (0D)
LE (0S)
); } }
